<BODY>
 AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of Saturday, May
1.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ENTERTAINMENT &LR;  (``e'' code)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; IDEAS PAGE &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MORAL-HAZARD (Undated) _ About two years ago, Matt Hazard and
