Schrenko is going to push for legislation requiring teachers to
carry pepper spray, tear gas and Tasers (a stun gun-like device).
(Cumming, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   SUV _ WASHINGTON _ Popular sport utility vehicles will have to
meet the same tougher emission rules as cars under ambitious
pollution standards to be proposed by the Clinton administration.
Oil refiners will have to make cleaner gasoline, too. (Nesmith, Cox
News Service)
