</P>
<P>
   EDs: First pitch is at 7:40 p.m. EDT.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-BRAVES-NOTES01 _ ATLANTA _ Braves notebook. (Rogers, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
<P>
   KENTUCKY DERBYRAC-BISHER-DERBY _ LOUISVILLE, Ky. _ Furman Bisher
column from the Kentucky Derby. This is Bisher's 50th derby.
(Bisher, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   RAC-TEAMS-DERBY _ LOUISVILLE, Ky. _ Tag teams: The Derby used to
be about bringing your one horse and hoping for the best. Today,
it's about trainers and wealthy owners bringing multiple entries _
or teams _ into the race, thus increasing their chances for victory
and using each of their horses as strategic chess pieces to change
the outcome of the race. (Crittenden, Palm Beach Post). 18.
</P>
<P>
   RAC-ARCHDEACON-DERBY01 _ LOUISVILLE, Ky. _ Blowout on trainer
Bob Baffert, who is the hottest thing in racing.The silver-tongued
trainer has rosey luck. He's won the last two Derbys and is going
for a record third win. He has 2 to 4 entries for Sat's field.
Story on his life and times and what he has done for sport.
(Archdeacon, Dayton Daily News). 30.
</P>
