<TEXT>
<P>
   ATTN EDITORS: The Brussels, Belgium-datelined story,
BC-KOSOVO-SPIN-NYT, by Craig R. Whitney, has been HELD. Please
guard against premature release. We will send an advisory when the
story is released for publication.
</P>
<P>
   Repeat: BC-KOSOVO-SPIN-NYT is HELD.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service, April 30.
</P>
